Description: KFL stack utilities (development files)
 Headers, static archive, and unversioned .so symlink for libk26util.

Package: libk26m3d0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KFL 3-D linear algebra (runtime)
 Vectors, matrices, quaternions, and rigid-body math. Pure C,
 deterministic floating-point (-ffp-contract=off + -fexcess-precision=
 standard), zero runtime dependency beyond libm. The substrate library
 for the astro suite and any K26 program needing fixed-size vec/mat
 math.

