Package:libk26astro-ephem0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KFL JPL ephemeris ingest (runtime)
 Chebyshev polynomial evaluator, DAF/SPK Type 2 binary kernel reader,
 high-throughput query with per-body LRU cache for sub-millisecond
 repeat queries. Designed for light-time correction loops.

