Package:libk26astro-conics0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KFL two-body conic mechanics (runtime)
 Universal-variable Kepler propagator, single- and multi-revolution
 Lambert solver, sphere-of-influence hierarchy. Pure functional - no
 global state, no integration loops.

