Package:libk26astro-grav0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KFL N-body integrators + perturbations (runtime)
 WHFast, IAS15 (Gauss-Radau), DKD Velocity Verlet integrators. J2
 oblateness, solar radiation pressure with conical shadow, GR PPN-1
 (Schwarzschild EIH) perturbations. Close-encounter detector for the
 MERCURIUS hybrid integrator.

