Package:libk26astro-rt0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libgfortran5, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KFL astrodynamics runtime manager (runtime)
 Composes K26AstroGravState plus the ephem/frame/conics machinery into
 a single K26AstroWorld opaque type. Multi-rate scheduler, MERCURIUS
 hybrid integrator, observer light-time / aberration, versioned binary
 snapshot format.

